Learning Outcome: Compare confidence produced by analytics to confidence provided by experts

Data is not infallible and either are humans. There is a difference between information based on expert opinion and information based on data analyses. Being able to fluidly move between these two types of information identifying strengths and weaknesses is a necessary professional and life skill.  How do you assess analytical confidence versus expert opinion now? What are the strengths and weaknesses of your current process? What would you change after taking this class?

Your post should be around 6-8 sentences long with a clear topic sentence at the beginning of each paragraph. 

Please add citations of lecture material or outside sources to add a broader expertise and knowledge base to your argument.

